I am twenty five years old, got three children and I am living in [town] in a quarter, I am a soildger and I am very happy. The three children are at school and there names are, [male name], [male name], and [female name], one is tow years old, one is three yers old, and one is eighteen month old. I am up to get ready to go on parade with the soigers, we have to get up at five o'clock in a morning and polish are boots, blanko are* belt and uniform and tiedy are beds up it is very hard work but you lern a lot about guns and we all get a bery good pay. We get as much food as we want and, we put three quarters of are money in the bank, because we get all the things nerly allway's cheap*.  Words: 146
